00:35:44,272 --> 00:36:05,116
As we're moving forward looking at this particular option, and really with all of the options aside from A and B, the A.1 and the B.1.2 options, where we don't have the ability to sort of work around the existing building, we are looking for ways to minimize or eliminate the need for the modular classrooms.

