00:37:15,927 --> 00:37:22,512
visual would have to be below the field potentially or as a parking garage that's illustrated here, a vertical above grade.

276
00:37:23,453 --> 00:37:29,517
We certainly will have the option of looking at and talking about what it would mean to do at-grade parking.

