00:50:13,940 --> 00:50:15,541
That's our vocational programming.

388
00:50:16,142 --> 00:50:22,507
So when we say the word comprehensive, not all high schools are comprehensive because not all high schools have vocational programming.

389
00:50:23,127 --> 00:50:24,810
To date, we have 15 CTE programs.

390
00:50:31,202 --> 00:50:32,143
increasing that.

391
00:50:32,343 --> 00:50:36,185
So by the end of this project, we will be adding four more.

