00:53:29,801 --> 00:53:51,793
I think through this work and in our educational plan, the other two pieces that we have that don't exist currently at Medford High School but that we would like to see expand is by bringing our preschool programming that's housed at two of our elementary schools, currently the Missittuck and the Brooks,

