414
00:54:18,458 --> 00:54:23,823
And then additionally to that, we have our therapeutic day program, Curtis Tufts High School.

415
00:54:24,860 --> 00:54:30,305
That is located in South Medford by Tufts Pool and Tufts Park.

416
00:54:30,905 --> 00:54:52,443
We would be also bringing that program up here to co-locate with some other programs that would allow, again, for the pooling of resources and the really true inclusion of all of our students so that our Curtis Tufts students also would have some increased opportunities for enrichment and education.

